snippet.title: Dead by Daylight x Dungeons & Dragons - Official Chapter Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's the Dead by Daylight x Dungeons & Dragons chapter reveal trailer. Dead by Daylight is an asymmetrical action multiplayer game developed by Behaviour Interactive. Players will soon be able to play a new chapter based on the iconic Dungeons & Dragons tabletop game. The new chapter brings the legendary Vecna as a killer in the game alongside The Bard as a new survivor. The Dead by Daylight Dungeons & Dragons chapter is launching on June 3.

#DeadByDaylight #DungeonsAndDragons #Gaming
